<section>
    <header>Inspiration</header>
    <p>Inspiration allows you to get advantage on any roll. It is exclusively given out as a treat by the dungeon master. Here is what you need to know:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Inspiration must be used in the same session as it was given (No hoarding!)</li>
        <li>Inspiration will almost always be given out if you correct the dungeon master on a rule</li>
        <li>Inspiration will almost always be given out for out-of-the-box, clever, thinking</li>
        <li>Inspiration will almost always be given out for kickass roleplaying as your character</li>
        <li>Inspiration will only be given out for amazing rule-of-cool situations</li>
        <li>Inspiration will never be given out for sitting on your phone</li>
    </ul>
